headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Cboe Global Markets (CBOE) After Its Strong Multi‑Year Rally?
summary: If you are wondering whether Cboe Global Markets shares are priced attractively right now, it helps to start with what the recent returns and current valuation score are actually telling you. The stock last closed at US$260.95, with returns of 5.2% over the past week, 3.9% over the last 30 days, 5.2% year to date, 38.3% over 1 year, 117.7% over 3 years and 189.7% over 5 years.
